<includeonly>{{#switch:{{{value|0}}}
| 0 =
| 1 = ★☆☆☆☆ (1/5)
| 2 = ★★☆☆☆ (2/5)
| 3 = ★★★☆☆ (3/5)
| 4 = ★★★★☆ (4/5)
| 5 = ★★★★★ (5/5)
| #default = {{{value|}}}/5
}}</includeonly><noinclude>
Value renderer for 1-5 ratings. Emits filled/empty Unicode stars with
the numeric value in parentheses. Set at the property level on
`Has rating` so every review inherits this rendering automatically —
you'll see it in the Review subobject rows on [[Dune]].

Parameters:
* value - Integer rating 0-5 (other values fall through to `N/5`).
</noinclude>
